    "prica": {
        "naslov": "Our Story",
        "sadrzaj1": "Paw of Happiness was founded in 2015 by a group of volunteers who wanted to help abandoned animals on the streets of Belgrade. What started as fostering for a few dogs, today has grown into one of the largest adoption associations in Serbia.",
        "sadrzaj2": "Our team consists of passionate animal lovers, veterinarians, trainers, and volunteers who work daily to give every animal a chance for a happy life. So far, we have successfully adopted over 200 dogs and cats, and we care for about 30 animals in our shelter every day.",
        "sadrzaj3": "We believe that every animal deserves love, attention, and a safe home. Our mission is to provide that through adoption programs, education, and support for new owners.",
        "misijaNaslov": "Our Mission",
        "misijaSadrzaj": "Provide shelter, care and love to abandoned animals and find them responsible and caring owners.",
        "vizijaNaslov": "Our Vision",
        "vizijaSadrzaj": "A world where there are no abandoned animals and where every pet is treated as a family member."
    },
